lead_paragraph: Six medalists from the 2008 Beijing Games had their medals stripped by the International Olympic Committee on Wednesday after they tested positive for banned substances in re-tests of their samples, the IOC said.

headline.print_headline: Six Beijing Games Medalists Among Nine More Positive Re-Tests
